&quot;Also, I don&#39;t get why anyone who is a skeptic would belong to this group?&quot;

I am here because I want to see what its all about, ask questions, and form
my own conclusions. I can&#39;t have an opinion on something if I don&#39;t even
know what it is about. So I am here to learn about ITC technologies from
both believers and other skeptics alike.

I am not here to debunk or otherwise tear apart anything Frank is doing, and
my opinion should not matter to him.

I am here to hopefully find proof one way or another.

Some people here have very bad baggage associated with skeptics. A true
skeptic neither believes, nor disbelieves anything without proof either way.
There are people who won&#39;t believe anything no matter what proof you give
them. They are not true skeptics. They are disbelievers, the flip side of
believers.

Skeptics should be square in the middle. Skeptics think only objectively.


